{
  "texts": [
    "\"Your father is wise.",
    "I think I needed to hear that.\"",
    "The boy grinned and ran off to join his friends, leaving Jonah to contemplate the child's words.",
    "Mercy, indeed, was a difficult concept to grasp, especially when it seemed to contradict justice.",
    "But perhaps, that was the beauty of it -God's ways were higher than humans', and His thoughts were beyond comprehension."
  ]
}